# Selenium SauceDemo Automation

This repository contains Selenium automation tests for the SauceDemo website, created as part of a Software Testing assignment.

## Project Scope
- Automated login test
- Automated checkout form validation
- Basic CI/CD integration using GitHub Actions
- Static code analysis using SonarCloud

## Tools Used
- Python
- Selenium WebDriver
- GitHub Actions
- SonarCloud

## How to Run Tests Locally
```bash
python test_login.py
python test_checkout_validation.py
